Intere&s;t to be hone&s;t;'</Q> or el&s;e, Sir, &s;aid I, your Wall 
<Q REND="inline">'would have been as tedious a Piece of 
<PB N="79" REF="86"> Work as <HI>Penelope</HI>'s Web, if all that was done in
